Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "Under Kamala Harris, it has been one disaster after another — After Kamala cast the tie-breaking votes on the bills that caused the worst inflation in decades, the Harris price hikes have cost the typical Nevada family more than $32,000 dollars.""Now Kamala is promising communist price controls on food. Her plan will cause catastrophic inflation, shortages, and rationing— the restaurant industry will be obliterated."
